description:
A great show for little kids, about 2-5 - very peaceful and pleasant. Based on the Maurice Sendak books. I downloaded a few of these about 2 years ago, and ripped the rest from library DVDs and VHS tapes. Decent quality - the preschoolers definitely won\'t mind!
